questions.question: What would you do if you already had a workspace open and wanted to compare it to another?
options: Drag and drop the other workspace onto the Canvas.
Make changes to the workspace and view the differences in your version control system.

questions.question: Which of the follow changes would not appear in the Workspace Comparison window?
options: A MapInfo TAB writer feature type was deleted.
The workspace Overview parameter was changed.

questions.question: When merging workspaces, you can choose to merge a selection of changes instead of all changes.
